Python3.13 install Ubuntu

03 July 2025
09:17

Install:
	1. sudo add-apt-repository ppa:deadsnakes/ppa
	2. sudo apt install python3.13-full
	3. python3.13 --version
	4. python3.13 -m ensurepip --upgrade

Uninstall:
For Python 3.13 installed from PPA, open terminal and run command to remove it:

	1. sudo apt remove --autoremove python3.13
	2. sudo add-apt-repository --remove ppa:deadsnakes/ppa
